songs.title: New One
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Matthew Bellamy]
Yeah it's bugging me
Strangling me
And twisting me around
Yeah I'm endlessly
Caving in
And turning inside out

[Chorus: Matthew Bellamy]
Cause I want you now
I want you now
Give me your heart and your soul
Cause I want you now
I want you now
Give me complete control

[Verse 2: Matthew Bellamy]
It's grating me
Fooling me (?)
And forcing me to strive
To be endlessly
Caving in
And dreaming I'm alive

[Chorus: Matthew Bellamy]
And I want you now
I want you now
Give me your heart and your soul
Cause I want you now
I want you now
Give me complete control
